    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113330/extras/2fed4bfa52b3672961518fb8e31338b6.poster.avif?t=1771766694\" width=650 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113330/extras/2fed4bfa52b3672961518fb8e31338b6.webm?t=1771766694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113330/extras/2fed4bfa52b3672961518fb8e31338b6.mp4?t=1771766694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113330/extras/dc4a30a914229e574af03454f56fecdb.webp?t=1771766694\" width=252 height=38 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Space Cleaners is an online co-op horror game where you and up to 6 friends are A.I. units building a space cleaning business. Accept contracts from space corporations, scrub the goo off filthy stations, and survive hostility long enough to finish the job.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113330/extras/fdc3a863c77f6c4281964cad589e4e05.poster.avif?t=1771766694\" width=650 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113330/extras/fdc3a863c77f6c4281964cad589e4e05.webm?t=1771766694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113330/extras/fdc3a863c77f6c4281964cad589e4e05.mp4?t=1771766694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113330/extras/a5fc01194570f6d821f54bebdd760060.webp?t=1771766694\" width=309 height=39 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The dangers inside and outside the stations will try to stop you. But you can't back off; the business isn't going to grow itself. Buy equipment, save your crew, and do everything possible to keep your reputation intact. Clean the goo. Dodge the threats. Stay in business.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113330/extras/09028452ece2189cb3910b08110e9fad.poster.avif?t=1771766694\" width=650 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113330/extras/09028452ece2189cb3910b08110e9fad.webm?t=1771766694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113330/extras/09028452ece2189cb3910b08110e9fad.mp4?t=1771766694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113330/extras/fac2d0869439214cdcdeb9665569c02a.webp?t=1771766694\" width=516 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endure hostilities until the last goo is cleaned. Do not let the business die. Every job funds the next. Every loss sets you back.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113330/extras/647d25fb737da81e859c4d020c410978.webp?t=1771766694\" width=245 height=48 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Co-op up to 6 players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Physics based characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Proximity voice chat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedural generated maps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Robot customization</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully acknowledged as a space janitor</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
